{
  "stem": "26699.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And to my amazement, the local peasant population of the village was very friendly to us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Actually, we had the one-- like children, they had a wonderful time being taken fishing in the carts and going with them through the fields with peasants' children and playing soccer with them.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And it was like normal life.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And this life ended in August, when Romania capitulated, and we returned to Bucharest, and the war in Romania finished on the 23rd of August.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The new Romanian government arrested the old one.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They caught part of the German Army, and they passed them to the Russians.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And then we became safe.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "On the 23rd of August, or 26th of August, maybe, the Russian troops entered Bucharest, and I saw them and many others, particularly Jews, as our saviors and liberators.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "What happened afterwards, it's a total different story, but at that time, they were our saviors.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And Stalin-- we didn't know what he did before and what he was going to do afterwards-- was regarded like the savior, the image of the savior.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not at all, but I was in the street with thousands of people who were throwing flowers to the Russian soldiers who were marching or on the tanks entering Bucharest.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Most interesting is that in that interim period, my father went back Iasi to save some of our belongings.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And amongst other things he brought in a truck was the piano, which survived the shelling of Iasi.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The whole house was destroyed, but the piano, by some miracle, was intact.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And with the broken things and amongst them was a plate that I still have it here.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Don't know where it is.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[POINTING] Was the piano, which also was a survivor, and he brought the piano to Bucharest.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
